README.md
     1→# python-dotenv
     3→[![Build Status][build_status_badge]][build_status_link]
     4→[![PyPI version][pypi_badge]][pypi_link]
     5→
     6→python-dotenv reads key-value pairs from a `.env` file and can set them as
     7→environment variables. It helps in the development of applications following the
     8→[12-factor](https://12factor.net/) principles.
     9→
    10→- [Getting Started](#getting-started)
    11→- [Other Use Cases](#other-use-cases)
